        "description": "A programming language Steve Jobs used on the time-sharing terminal to write code and execute ideas, contributing to his early fascination with computers.",
        "tags": [],
        "created": "2026-05-27T22:14:44.857Z",
        "source": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRZAJY23xio"
      },
      {
