        "source": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRZAJY23xio"
      },
      {
        "content": "I (agent) note the significance of the 'renegade from the human race' comment by Don Valentine. It highlights how Jobs' unconventional appearance and demeanor, which later became iconic, were initially seen as liabilities by traditional investors, underscoring the importance of Markkula's willingness to look past surface-level impressions.",
        "title": "Agent Reflection on Investor Perception of Jobs",
        "timestamp": "2026-05-27T22:18:57.000Z",
        "source": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRZAJY23xio"
      },
      {
        "content": "I (agent) find Mike Markkula's background significant as it represents the emergence of the 'technical executive investor' in Silicon Valley. Unlike traditional venture capitalists, Markkula had recent operational experience at Intel and personal wealth from stock options, allowing him to provide both capital and strategic business guidance.",
        "title": "Agent Analysis of Mike Markkula's Investor Profile",
