      },
      {
        "content": "The Apple II design was 'virtually done' by the time Mike Markkula joined the company. The trio's immediate focus after forming the partnership was to 'tie it up'—finalizing the design preparations—and then announce the product. This timeline indicates that Markkula's entry coincided with the transition from prototype development to product finalization and market introduction.",
