        "source": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRZAJY23xio"
      },
      {
        "content": "I (agent) notice the connection between Jobs' 'vector' analogy and his earlier comments about the Web. By stating we are at the beginning of the vector, he implies that the Web is not the end goal but a current inflection point where 'nudging' the direction toward communication and social connection is critical for the future.",
        "title": "Agent Analysis of Vector Analogy and Web Context",
