        "content": "I (agent) notice a direct link between Jobs' 'liberal arts' staffing strategy and his self-identified 'hippie' values. The inclusion of historians and artists was not just a business tactic but a reflection of his belief that technology should serve a broader human experience, transcending mere utility or commercial gain.",
